  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This use-results post-marketing surveillance (PMS) study for Sovaldi® tablets (sofosbuvir,
      SOF) administered in combination with Rebetol® capsules (ribavirin, REB) will evaluate the
      safety and efficacy of SOF administered in combination with ribavirin under real world use in
      Japan. Among adult patients with chronic genotype 2 hepatitis C virus (HCV) infection and
      treated with SOF+ribavirin in routine clinical use, the primary objective of this study is to
      evaluate the incidence of adverse drug reactions (ADRs) under real world settings.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
